		sample = s_v_a7_Ghage_01;
		screen_text = "Umberteen sent you? What? Is this true? You have his book-it MUST be so... Such a brave and selfless path he took. I must request your assistance, traveler. I have discovered where the Droc come from, and the Howlers and many of the other beasts that have plagued our pilgrimage...";
